desc: Are you looking for wine delivery? The Wine Feed Downtown Raleigh provides deliveries to Raleigh, Durham, and the surrounding areas. Call us today!

layout.text: Your Trusted Raleigh + Durham Wine People

We are currently OPEN for retail shopping, patio service, and wine bar service at both our Raleigh and Durham stores. Our amazing team is dedicated to providing inspiring selections of wines from around the world paired with great service.
We are updating gift options weekly, we can special order your favorite wines, and will deliver all over the Triangle! We also ship to anywhere in NC, VA, DC, and FL via UPS.
